data.description:
Low Maintenance Brick + Mainly One Level Living
A rare find in this community. This brick home is ideal for several LIFESTYLES. As you enter, you'll appreciate the features and lovely details this mainly one level home offers. Hitchcock ceilings, wainscoting, volume ceilings, attractive moldings, and abundance of wood floors. A large foyer welcomes you to your great room also with access to a den/office or use your way and a gracious dining room. A gas fireplace with faux stonework takes center stage in the living room. The large, open kitchen offers the chef in the house space to cook with its extensive amount of granite counters & cabinetry, serving bar and stainless appliances, double oven, cook top and refrigerator, plus a delightful breakfast room; a wonderful place to start your day. Walk outside to a wonderful patio perfect for dining al fresco. The grounds and rear yard are easy care. Refresh and unwind in this grand primary suite, striking trey ceiling and large walk-in closet located on the main level. The primary bath offers tile, separate tiled shower, double bowl vanity and a relaxing jetted tub. This is a split bedroom plan arrangement. Two guest bedrooms each offering their own appeal with access to a lovely jack and jill bathroom on main level. The upstairs features a loft/ living room and bedroom with its own bathroom. The laundry room provides extra storage. There is an attached side load 2 car garage with parking space and garage door opener. 
The Ridge at Chukker Creek has lots of amenities to offer including a pool, lake and miles of walking trails. Bordered by horse farms, conservation land and golf courses. A tremendous offering...don't miss out on this Aiken HOME.
